text: Central Louisiana (Cenla), also known as the Crossroads, is the region of the U.S. state of Louisiana. == Parishes == Central Louisiana consists of the following 10 parishes: * Allen Parish * Beauregard Parish * Catahoula Parish * Concordia Parish * Grant Parish * La Salle Parish * Natchitoches Parish * Rapides Parish * Sabine Parish * Vernon Parish Category:Regions of Louisiana
title: Central Louisiana
